  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nThe `meshMessageDeliveriesThreshold` scoring params of `beacon_aggregate_and_proof` topic is 17.15638, the same to v0.36.0 while in v0.37.0 we filter a lot of AggregateAndProof messages due to #4019\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nAlthough there is no clear evidence that this downscore peers (#4084) as `beacon_aggregate_and_proof` p3 is fine, we should expect a smaller `meshMessageDeliveriesThreshold` scoring params as 70% of AggregateAndProof messages are filtered\r\n",
